There are specific considerations to be taken care of to upgrade the ratings of Tesla Inc.

The concerns are more of a qualitative nature not of a quantitative nature

If Tesla will have a broader vehicle line-up then shall it be regarded as a positive development

Rene goes on to give suggestions to upgrade the ratings; says it is possible only if Tesla-

Expands its global footprint;

Maintains a global solid competitive presence;

Improves Product Breadth;

Consistent and Prudent Financial Policy;

Possesses excellent liquidity including ample cash;





